(42078, 130054, 0, 1, '豆花少年之阿全的煩惱', '', '2012-01-10 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 4, '豆花少年之阿全的煩惱   \r\nA teenager (A-Chen) who’s got a problem with a lot of pimples \r\n\r\n\r\n豆花少年 叫做阿全\r\n長像不差 煩惱整臉\r\nA teenager (A-Chen) who had gotten in a problem with a lot of pimples. \r\nActually he was looking good but with a lot of pimples which was making him sad. \r\n\r\n心情不佳 指指點點 \r\n豆花少年 難過整天\r\nHe had such a bad mood because of his friends were teasing him. \r\nA-Chen felt sad every day. \r\n \r\n這只不過是青春作祟\r\n過了幾年它就會不見\r\nBut it is just a harmony from the puberty.\r\nIt will be gone after a couple of years later.\r\n\r\n就別再笑他豆花少年 \r\n那滿臉豆花是想擁抱戀愛的感覺\r\nDon’t tease him because of his pimple.\r\nThe pimple means how much he wanted to experience the love.  \r\n\r\n豆花少年 眼神無邪\r\n愛吃豆花 家住花蓮\r\nA-Chen had a lot of pimples but still with a pair of pure eyes.  \r\nHe likes to eat “Door-Hua” (it is kind of a popular liquid dessert among the student in Taiwan) and was born in Hualien. \r\n\r\n突然有天 街上遇見 \r\n轉身回頭 是蓮花小姐\r\nSomeday he bumped into a girl called “ Lien –Hua” on the street when she was twisted around.  A-Chen had a crush on her. \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n一見鍾情就開始曖昧\r\n每天通話也不厭倦\r\nThey started an ambiguous love after the first eye contact.  \r\nThey wouldn’t get bored even they had been on the phone all day long.\r\n\r\n這酸酸甜甜初戀滋味\r\n那情荳初開是他們十七歲的夏天\r\nIt was tasted kind of bitter-sweet.\r\nThe first love was happened in the summer in A-Chen’s 17th.\r\n\r\n那一個夏天 一起去的海邊\r\nThat summer the beach we went together.   \r\n\r\n\r\n那一個夏天 是我 人生第一個初戀\r\nThat summer was my first date with a girl.\r\n\r\n長大之後 豆花少年 \r\n沒了豆花 換住台北\r\nTime flew by, A-Chen was growing up. \r\nA- chen had moved to Taipei and There is no any pimples on his face.\r\n\r\n交了許多 漂亮美眉 \r\n漸漸忘了 初戀感覺  \r\nHe has been dating a lot of hot chicks.\r\nBut he is gradually forgetting how the first love it was. \r\n\r\n因為美眉就是愛你的錢 \r\n要是身無分文就踢到旁邊\r\nBecause of those hot chicks they all addicted to anything about the money.\r\nIf u don’t have money on your pocket, they’re going to kick u away. \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n這苦澀滋味男人一定了解 \r\n那黃湯下肚醒來又是重新的一天\r\nAs a men, u must understand that kind of feelings.\r\nAfter couple of drinks later, u get drunk then u wake up next day. It seems to nothing was happened. \r\n\r\n那酸酸甜甜初戀滋味\r\n是我們再也回不去的快樂從前 \r\nThe taste of that bitter-sweet first love is the past we can’t return to. ', '', 142, '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 1, '2012-01-10 01:07:32', '2013-10-07 17:20:03', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
